I"–<p>(MIT) Escreva um programa que conte o n√∫mero de vogais numa <em>string</em> <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">s</code> composta unicamente de letras min√∫sculas. Por exemplo, se <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">s = 'azcbobobegghakl'</code>, seu programa deve imprimir <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">N√∫mero de vogais: 5</code>.</p>

<!-- more -->

<h3 id="solu√ß√£o">Solu√ß√£o:</h3>
<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">s</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">input</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'Digite uma string de letras min√∫sculas: '</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="n">n</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span>
<span class="n">v</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">'aeiou'</span>

<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">letter</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">s</span><span class="p">:</span>
  <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">letter</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">v</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">n</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="mi">1</span>

<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">f'N√∫mero de vogais: </span><span class="si">{</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="si">}</span><span class="s">'</span><span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
